snippet.title: Ground Zero: India Tv's Exclusive Report On Uri Attack

localized.description:
Watch India TV's exclusive ground zero report on Uri attack. The 2016 Uri attack was an attack by four heavily armed terrorists on 18 September 2016, near the town of Uri in the Indian state of Jammu and Kashmir. It was reported as "the deadliest attack on security forces in Kashmir in two decades"
